The paper discusses a methodology for automatic summarization of documents, which falls under the category of natural language processing (cs.CL). The paper also mentions the use of a probabilistic model, which suggests a connection to information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper deals with the task of content determination, which is a common problem in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and information systems (cs.SI).
